name: #9 SIN
description: Hunters searched the 7 realms for Sin until they realized while they sought the mad king, Sin had found them. Trapped in an illusion, imprisoned in the maze of the Dark Catacombs. The King of the Abyss and his allure of darkness invites the feeble willed to sin into the Forbidden Catacombs. Their desperate cries remain unheard, only the bones serve as a memory of the lost hunters.
